# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:14
translate chinese mari13_8ff999a9:

    # "My phone starts buzzing in my pocket."
    "口袋里的手机开始震动。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:19
translate chinese mari13_cc03b1d7:

    # fr "Hey, [pcname]. I had a question for you. Do you know anything about cars?"
    fr "嘿，[pcname]。我有件事想问你。你懂点车吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:20
translate chinese mari13_988170b5:

    # pc "Just a little, why?"
    pc "懂一点，怎么了？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:22
translate chinese mari13_0aae16d6:

    # fr "Well, I have my dad's old truck out in the barn, and it's not running right now."
    fr "嗯，我爸爸那辆旧卡车还在谷仓里，现在开不了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:23
translate chinese mari13_180b4647:

    # fr "I thought maybe if I could get it running again, I could try to learn how to drive."
    fr "我想如果能把它修好，我或许可以试着学开车。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:24
translate chinese mari13_1eb798c6:

    # pc "Is that what you want? I thought you were afraid of cars."
    pc "这是你的打算吗？我还以为你怕车呢。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:26
translate chinese mari13_5a2e5dff:

    # fr "I am... but I think I need to move forward. My assistant veterinary position is in Whiterock, so I'm going to have to drive back and forth."
    fr "是啊……但我觉得我得向前迈进。我在怀特洛克的兽医助理工作，所以得开车往返。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:27
translate chinese mari13_ed288529:

    # fr "I don't want to have to rely on somebody else to take me all the time."
    fr "我不想总是依赖别人载我。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:28
translate chinese mari13_d64bc11a:

    # pc "That makes sense."
    pc "这很合理。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:30
translate chinese mari13_fa47ee6f:

    # fr "So, do you think you could come look at my truck and see if you can figure out what's wrong with it?"
    fr "那，你觉得能过来看看我的卡车，帮我查查哪里出问题了吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:31
translate chinese mari13_47996b5f:

    # pc "Sure, I'll come look."
    pc "当然，我过去看看。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:33
translate chinese mari13_4b7d8262:

    # fr "Thanks, [pcname]. See you in a little while."
    fr "谢谢，[pcname]。一会儿见。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:36
translate chinese mari13_0a3a1d94:

    # "I hang up and start driving out to Mari's farm."
    "我挂断电话，开车前往玛丽的农场。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:39
translate chinese mari13_86dfe7f8:

    # "When I get to Mari's house, we go out to the barn together and I pop the hood on the truck."
    "到了玛丽家，我们一起走到谷仓，我掀开了卡车的引擎盖。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:40
translate chinese mari13_14d2a400:

    # fr "Do you think you can fix it?"
    fr "你觉得能修好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:41
translate chinese mari13_1638d0b9:

    # pc "I can try. I'm sure the battery is dead, first of all. Let's take that out and get it charged."
    pc "我可以试试。首先，我敢肯定电池没电了。我们把它拆下来充充电吧。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:42
translate chinese mari13_118245c8:

    # pc "Do you have wrenches or a socket set or anything?"
    pc "你有扳手、套筒扳手之类的工具吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:43
translate chinese mari13_981633b9:

    # fr "I'm sure I do. There's a bunch of Dad's tools over here. I'll show you."
    fr "肯定有。这边有一大堆我爸的工具。我带你去看看。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:46
translate chinese mari13_9f27c930:

    # "Using her dad's old tools, I take the battery out of the truck and we drive it to a nearby autoparts store."
    "我用她爸爸的旧工具把卡车上的电瓶拆下来，然后我们开车去附近的汽车配件店。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:47
translate chinese mari13_48f63bf1:

    # "It ends up being bad, so Mari buys a new one, and we return to the truck once again."
    "结果电瓶确实坏了，于是玛丽买了个新的，我们又回到卡车旁。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:50
translate chinese mari13_25ce6fc4:

    # pc "Well, now it's getting power, but it's not turning over."
    pc "嗯，现在有电了，但发动机还是打不着火。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:51
translate chinese mari13_3173e3d2:

    # fr "What do you think it is? The pistons?"
    fr "你觉得是哪里的问题？活塞吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:52
translate chinese mari13_00123606:

    # pc "What makes you say that?"
    pc "你怎么这么说？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:53
translate chinese mari13_53ea273a:

    # fr "I don't know. It's just a car term I've heard before."
    fr "我也不知道。只是以前听过这个汽车术语。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:54
translate chinese mari13_d12b1362:

    # fr "I don't know anything about cars."
    fr "我对车一窍不通。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:55
translate chinese mari13_95134570:

    # pc "I'm not really sure what's causing it not to start at this point."
    pc "目前我也不太确定到底是什么原因导致它无法启动。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:60
translate chinese mari13_f47dff33:

    # "WARNING!"
    "警告！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:61
translate chinese mari13_66b8cb1f:

    # rj "Sorry to interrupt, but if you continue right now, you will miss a scene that you might want to see!"
    rj "抱歉打断一下，但如果你现在继续，你会错过一个你可能想看的场景！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:63
translate chinese mari13_793e8063:

    # rj "You can continue with this scene right now, but you will miss a threesome scene with Reba and Mari."
    rj "你可以现在继续这个场景，但你会错过丽芭和玛丽的三人行场景。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:64
translate chinese mari13_908919a8:

    # rj "To get the threesome scene you need to have had sex with Reba before inviting her over to fix Mari's truck."
    rj "要解锁三人行场景，你需要在邀请丽芭过来修理玛丽的卡车之前，先和她发生过关系。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:65
translate chinese mari13_0323a8c0:

    # rj "Are you sure you want to continue and miss the Mari/Reba threesome?"
    rj "你确定要继续并错过玛丽和丽芭的三人行吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:69
translate chinese mari13_380064ab:

    # rj "Okay then! No complaining online that you missed it!"
    rj "好吧！别在网上抱怨说你错过了哦！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:71
translate chinese mari13_e431e7a9:

    # rj "I'll leave and let you get back to the game now! Have fun!"
    rj "我这就走，让你回去继续玩游戏！玩得开心！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:74
translate chinese mari13_0d0f23dd:

    # pc "But I know somebody who might be able to help."
    pc "不过我认识一个人，说不定能帮上忙。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:76
translate chinese mari13_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mari_ohcool1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_ohcool1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:77
translate chinese mari13_d77b9f15:

    # fr "Oh, cool!"
    fr "哦，太棒了！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:78
translate chinese mari13_0dcccada:

    # pc "I'll call her real quick. Just a sec."
    pc "我马上给她打个电话。稍等一下。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:83
translate chinese mari13_9c77f5af:

    # rj "I thought so!"
    rj "我就知道！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:85
translate chinese mari13_90e9154b:

    # rj "For now we'll just act like we don't know anybody who can fix Mari's truck."
    rj "现在我们先假装不认识能修好玛丽卡车的人。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:86
translate chinese mari13_ac52c148:

    # rj "Then later, after you bone Reba, call Mari and tell her you know somebody who can help."
    rj "等会儿，等你和丽贝卡搞完之后，再给玛丽打电话，告诉她你认识能帮忙的人。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:88
translate chinese mari13_94d84e9b:

    # rj "Okay, I'm gonna get out of your way now. Have fun!"
    rj "好的，我这就让开。玩得开心！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:90
translate chinese mari13_0d0f23dd_1:

    # pc "But I know somebody who might be able to help."
    pc "不过我认识一个人，说不定能帮上忙。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:92
translate chinese mari13_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/mari_ohcool1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_ohcool1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:93
translate chinese mari13_d77b9f15_1:

    # fr "Oh, cool!"
    fr "哦，太棒了！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:94
translate chinese mari13_0dcccada_1:

    # pc "I'll call her real quick. Just a sec."
    pc "我马上给她打个电话。等一下。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:100
translate chinese mari13_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/mari_shoot1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_shoot1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:101
translate chinese mari13_f02bf9d0:

    # fr "Aw, shoot. Thank you for trying though."
    fr "哎呀，真倒霉。不过还是谢谢你帮忙了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:102
translate chinese mari13_3c47ccd7:

    # pc "If I think of something, I'll let you know. Hopefully we can get it fixed sometime."
    pc "如果我想到了什么办法，我会告诉你。希望以后能修好它。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:103
translate chinese mari13_de92dcbb:

    # fr "Yeah, I'd really like to. I guess I could have a mechanic tow it to a shop, but I know that'll be expensive."
    fr "是啊，我真的很想修好它。我想我可以找个修车师傅把它拖到修理厂，但我知道那会很贵。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:104
translate chinese mari13_276f10a0:

    # fr "Anyway, thanks for the help!"
    fr "不管怎样，谢谢你的帮忙！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:107
translate chinese mari13_5497b15e:

    # "Mari and I say our goodbyes and I leave. I wish I could have got that truck running for her."
    "我和玛丽道别后离开了。真希望我能帮她把那辆卡车修好。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:108
translate chinese mari13_a3af5f30:

    # "I'm not sure what to do at this point. Maybe I'll come across a solution later."
    "现在我也不确定该怎么办。也许以后我会想到解决办法。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:115
translate chinese mari13phone_93ed8dd4:

    # pc "I think I might know somebody who could help with your truck."
    pc "我觉得我可能认识一个人，能帮你修卡车。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:118
translate chinese mari13phone_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mari_ohcool1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_ohcool1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:119
translate chinese mari13phone_e48ada16:

    # fr "Oh, cool! That would be great."
    fr "哦，太好了！那太棒了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:120
translate chinese mari13phone_28ca97d1:

    # pc "Okay, I'll call her real quick. Just a sec."
    pc "好的，我马上给她打个电话。等一下。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:127
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_589dd85f:

    # pc "Hey, Reba? You busy?"
    pc "喂，瑞芭？你忙吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:128
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_c6aaa4b5:

    # rb "Naw, what's up?"
    rb "不忙，怎么了？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:129
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_6033c0b7:

    # pc "I have a friend whose truck isn't starting and I was wondering..."
    pc "我有个朋友的卡车打不着火，我想问问……"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:131
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_c2ea06eb:

    # rb "Gimme the address and I'm on my way!"
    rb "给我地址，我马上过去！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:132
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_a8e3c862:

    # pc "Haha, okay."
    pc "哈哈，好的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:135
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_ee70a372:

    # "I give Reba directions to Mari's farm and a few minutes later she meets us there."
    "我给丽贝卡指了去玛丽农场的路，几分钟后她就到了那里。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:138
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_05b2461c:

    # rb "Oh my God! Your dogs are {i}so{/i} cute."
    rb "天哪！你的狗{i}好{/i}可爱。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:139
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_22df0ba2:

    # fr "They seem to like you."
    fr "它们好像挺喜欢你的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:140
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_68c9b491:

    # rb "What's their names?"
    rb "它们叫什么名字？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:142
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mari_appaandmomo.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_appaandmomo.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:143
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_0ede8f0a:

    # fr "The big one is Appa, and the little guy is Momo."
    fr "大的叫阿帕，小的叫莫莫。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:144
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_b4839da7:

    # rb "Oh my God, I love them!"
    rb "天哪，我太喜欢它们了！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:147
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_34d27c0e:

    # rb "You didn't tell me that I was fixin' this car for a cute girlfriend of yours, [pcname]."
    rb "你之前没告诉我，我修这辆车是为了你那个可爱的女朋友，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:148
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_be9414f2:

    # pc "Oh, sorry."
    pc "哦，抱歉。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:149
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_380ac7ef:

    # rb "Naw, it's no problem, I'm just messin'."
    rb "没关系，我只是开个玩笑。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:151
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_f7c6563e:

    # rb "Aw, hey I remember you from the burger place."
    rb "哎呀，我在汉堡店见过你。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:152
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_11d0fe17:

    # fr "Hey, yeah that's me."
    fr "嘿，对，就是我。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:154
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_2acf7aec:

    # rb "I'm Reba, by the way."
    rb "顺便说一下，我是丽芭。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:155
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_6f785a5d:

    # fr "Hello. I'm Mari. Nice to meet you."
    fr "你好。我是玛丽。很高兴认识你。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:156
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_a9aba0f6:

    # rb "Okay, let's see what this thing is doing."
    rb "好，我们来看看这车怎么回事。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:159
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_1a16e9d4:

    # rb "So how long you say it's been sitting here?"
    rb "你说这车在这里停了多久了？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:160
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_8ebf8623:

    # fr "About four years."
    fr "大概四年。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:161
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_90a271fa:

    # rb "Alright, and y'all replaced the battery already, so that's good."
    rb "好的，你们已经换过电瓶了，这很好。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:162
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_22d6811f:

    # rb "I'm gonna try a few things, but I expect we'll have to change the gas in the tank, because it's probably gone bad."
    rb "我打算试几个方法，但估计得把油箱里的汽油换掉，因为可能已经变质了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:163
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_2dc05954:

    # rb "And I'll clean out the air filter and change the oil and might have to replace the fuel pump too."
    rb "我还会清理空气滤清器、更换机油，可能还得换个燃油泵。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:164
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_1bccde91:

    # rb "Then after all that, if the engine starts, we'll have to get those tires aired up. They don't look like they've rotted, which is good. Hopefully they'll still hold air."
    rb "等这些都搞定后，如果发动机能启动，我们还得给轮胎充气。轮胎看起来没腐烂，这倒不错。希望它们还能保持气压。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:168
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/mari_shoot1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_shoot1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:169
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_8f74c366:

    # fr "Aw, shoot. How much is all of that going to cost?"
    fr "哎呀，糟了。这些总共要多少钱？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:170
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_8f3b3d9a:

    # rb "I can get you a new fuel pump for about $100. New oil filter and oil is like $30. Then just a tank of gas to replace the old junk."
    rb "我给你弄个新燃油泵大概100美元。新机油滤清器和机油大概30美元。然后只要加满一箱油把旧的换掉就行。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:171
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_428bb652:

    # rb "And all the labor is on the house, because I like that guy over there, and you seem like a pretty cool chick too."
    rb "而且所有工时费我包了，因为我挺喜欢那边那个小伙子，而且你看起来也是个挺酷的姑娘。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:172
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_3eeb60d9:

    # rb "Y'all just gotta hang out and keep me company and hand me junk when I ask for it, alright?"
    rb "你们只要陪着我，在我需要的时候递点东西给我就行，行吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:174
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/mari_surething2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_surething2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:175
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_9af4e82f:

    # fr "Sure thing!"
    fr "没问题！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:178
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_ab992a3c:

    # rb "So you don't drive?"
    rb "所以你不会开车？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:179
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_205c26d0:

    # fr "No, I haven't ever learned. My parents were killed in a car accident and I've been kind of scared of them since then."
    fr "不会，我从来没学过。我父母死于车祸，从那以后我就有点怕车。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:180
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_b0f6c8c0:

    # rb "Aw dang, I'm sorry. My daddy's gone too. I know it hurts."
    rb "哎呀，真抱歉。我爸爸也去世了。我知道那种痛。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:181
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_254e65aa:

    # fr "Yeah it does. But I'm ready to learn how to drive now. I think I need to."
    fr "是啊，很痛。但我现在准备学开车了。我觉得我得学。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:182
translate chinese mari13rebahelp_d2c576b2:

    # rb "Yeah, we'll get this truck going and you can drive all over the place."
