    # fr "You're not a burden, honey. You've already helped me a ton, just by fixing the truck."
    fr "你不是负担，亲爱的。 光是修好那辆卡车，你就已经帮了我大忙了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:608
translate chinese marirebathreesome_077c1928:

    # rb "Okay. Ooh, I'm so excited."
    rb "好的。哦，我太兴奋了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:611
translate chinese marirebathreesome_c4ad767e:

    # "After breakfast, we all have to go our separate ways."
    "吃完早餐后，我们大家都要各奔东西了。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:612
translate chinese marirebathreesome_b54afa55:

    # "We say our goodbyes, promising that we'd get together again soon."
    "我们道别时，都承诺很快会再聚。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:613
translate chinese marirebathreesome_50a1b160:

    # "I can't wait. I knew that Reba and Mari could be friends if they spent some time together, but I never expected things to go this well."
    "我等不及了。我知道如果瑞芭和玛丽多相处一段时间，她们肯定能成为朋友，但我真没想到事情会进展得这么顺利。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:614
translate chinese marirebathreesome_1d69eda0:

    # "What a night."
    "真是个难忘的夜晚。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:629
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_71cd923e:

    # fr "I kind of like that you're so into me that you don't want anybody else."
    fr "我挺喜欢你这么迷恋我，甚至不愿考虑别人。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:630
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_48f2c5d2:

    # fr "Even enough to turn down something like that."
    fr "甚至愿意为了我拒绝那种机会。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:633
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_9a6e995f:

    # rb "Oh um... sorry, I didn't mean to interrupt."
    rb "哦，那个……抱歉，我不是故意打断的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:634
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_13718e0d:

    # fr "Oh it's okay. Food's ready. Let's eat."
    fr "哦，没关系。饭做好了。我们开动吧。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:637
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_cf649c03:

    # "Mari cooks us a delicious dinner, then we three sit and eat together."
    "玛丽为我们做了一顿美味的晚餐，然后我们三个人坐在一起吃。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:638
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_d7ae222c:

    # "While we eat, Mari and Reba get to know each other more."
    "吃饭时，玛丽和丽贝卡进一步互相了解。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:639
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_f7bcdb44:

    # "They talk about their pasts, their jobs, their goals."
    "她们聊起各自的过往、工作以及人生目标。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:642
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_cb6680c9:

    # "Then, once dinner is over, we say goodbye to Reba."
    "晚餐结束后，我们向瑞芭道别。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:643
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_75e761e7:

    # fr "You sure I can't pay you something for the work?"
    fr "你确定不用我付点报酬吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:644
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_ac069b35:

    # rb "Oh naw, that's alright. I liked working on it and hanging out with y'all."
    rb "哦，不用了，没关系。我很喜欢做这个，也喜欢和大家在一起。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:645
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_8cca2575:

    # rb "And the food was great too."
    rb "而且饭菜也特别好吃。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:646
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_8efa9ce0:

    # fr "Alright. Well, you have my number if you ever want to talk or hang out or something."
    fr "好的。那，如果你想聊天或者约出来玩什么的，我有你的号码。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:647
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_0e8fd69e:

    # fr "I could always use a new girl friend."
    fr "我总是需要交个新女朋友的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:648
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_8e3a433a:

    # rb "Oh yeah, we should do something sometime. That'd be fun."
    rb "哦对，我们改天应该约个聚会。那会很有趣。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:650
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mari_surething2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_surething2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:651
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_9af4e82f:

    # fr "Sure thing!"
    fr "没问题！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:652
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_97bf71f7:

    # rb "Alright, I'll see y'all later. Have a good night!"
    rb "好吧，回头见。晚安！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:653
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_e7b02c91:

    # pc "You too, Reba. Thanks again!"
    pc "你也一样，瑞芭。再次感谢！"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:657
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/mari_comeinside1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_comeinside1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:658
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_3d089295:

    # fr "So... do you want to come inside and spend some time with me?"
    fr "那么……你想进来陪我待会儿吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:663
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_9bd5a025:

    # "I go inside with her and help her clean up the kitchen, then things quickly lead to her bedroom."
    "我跟着她进了屋，帮她收拾厨房，随后事情很快就发展到了她的卧室。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:672
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/mari_aww2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_aww2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:673
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_e10a3ba0:

    # fr "Aw alright. I'll see you later then, [pcname]."
    fr "“好吧。那回头见，[pcname]。”"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:676
translate chinese mari13nothreesome_cb6284dc:

    # "We say our goodbyes and I get in my car and drive away."
    "我们道别后，我上了车，开车离开了。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:3
    old "The weekend after you go with Mari to the cemetery to visit her parents, she will call you asking for your help."
    new "在你陪玛丽去墓地探望她父母的那个周末之后，她会打电话给你寻求帮助。"

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:4
    old "You can only help her with her problem after you have learned about Reba's job. At that point, you can call Mari on the weekend and tell her that you have a friend who could help. Both Reba and Mari's hearts need to be turned on."
    new "只有在你了解了丽贝卡的工作情况后，才能帮她解决问题。到那时，你可以在周末给玛丽打电话，告诉她有个朋友能帮忙。 雷巴和玛丽的心都需要被点燃。"

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:240
